faq.info_card_text_1: If there is any bleeding, even a small amount, please consult an ophthalmologist as soon as possible.
faq.info_card_text_2: If you feel any distortion in your vision or if the bleeding is more than usual, please consult an ophthalmologist.
faq.paragraph_1: The first sheet is until the 5th day of menstruation, and from the second sheet onwards, start taking it after finishing the previous sheet.
faq.paragraph_2: Set an alarm so that you can take it at the same time every day.
